Transcription.Text: Practical. The practical application of the above idea will involve considerable experimentation before it can be realised. Possible materials are zirconia stabilised with lime and thoria doped with rare earth oxides. If such a material can be made with these properties a possible way in which the cell may be incorporated in a sodium circuit is depicted in Fig. 4.
